Enum ColorPalette

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ColorPalette>
      • vistra.framework.util.palette.ColorPalette
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ColorPalette>

    public enum ColorPalette
extends java.lang.Enum<ColorPalette>
    A palette defining some customized colors. Use the lower-case constants for getting directly a Color.
    Author:
    Roland Bruggmann (brugr9@bfh.ch)
    See Also:
    FontPalette, StrokePalette, ShapePalette
